snippet.title: Human Resource Machine - Official Trailer #1
snippet.description:
Program little office workers to solve puzzles. Be a good employee! The machines are coming... for your job. http://tomorrowcorporation.com/humanresourcemachine

From the designers of World of Goo, Little Inferno, and Henry Hatsworth.

Made by Kyle, Kyle, and Allan at http://TomorrowCorporation.com
Original music by Kyle Gabler.

Soundtrack now available free! http://tomorrowcorporation.com/human-resource-machine-soundtrack
